text:
I remember watching a Minecraft stream most of a year ago where Gura talked about chatting with Shion, and gushed about how cute she was. About wanting to collab with her, but being worried about not being able to communicate well. Now, after so much waiting,  it finally happened, and they had more trouble with the minecarts than they did talking to one another.

This was actually immeasurable levels of cute, precious and hilarious. Things have been so exciting lately with the server merge bringing different branches together, but this is really something else. The language difference wasn't a barrier in this collab so much as it was an opportunity for smiles and laughs. I feel like a proud parent watching a kid go on their first date, and a wingman watching his friend get together with the cute girl they've had a crush on for ages. 

But more than anything, I'm a chumbud proud as heck of a little shark who's come so very far and become such a special idol. It might be a little strange to have an idol making so many chikubi and "pantsu misete" jokes...but she has a wife-to-be making just as many unchi jokes, so I think it all works out. <3
